pic1_alt: The hex logo for the datardis package. The logo consists of a blue police call box that resembles the TARDIS from Doctor Who, in a tunnel made of numbers and similar symbols. All is within a blue hexagon. Due to the 3D tunnel effect, the hexagon appears to be bigger on the inside.
pic2_alt: A proportional image from the 2023 Doctor Who 60th Anniversary event, featuring David Tennant as the 14th Doctor, and Catherine Tate as Donna Noble. They are facing the camera, with a rusted, decrepit white robot in the background. There is a hazy lens effect around them. The Doctor Who and BBC logos are superimposed at the bottom of the image.
